{"tid":473961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各種不合理的日本校規？","createTime":"2017-11-19T16:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T11:53:43.000Z","uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"941fd20a4cb317f06d6c304842b488b01eb8958c","tid":473961,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"深度文化談各種不合理的日本校規 <br />\n15.11.2017<br />\n <br />\n近這一年來，日本的不合理校規相繼上報，例如「因為可能挑起男性情慾而禁止綁馬尾」和「強行把學生頭髮染黑」，大眾開始討論校規的意義和過份規制的問題。在時事節目《NEWS23》播出「不合理校規」的特集後，更多網民在Twitter上分享學生時代遇到的不合理校規。只要在Twitter上搜尋「ブラック校則（黑心校規）」或者「こんな校則いらない（不需要這種校規）」就能找到很多網民的悲慘經歷。<br />\n<br />\n▼ 很喜歡滝季山影一諷刺染髮事件的作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/005201_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F005201_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2674188a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 「在游泳課時，體育老師跟生理期的女生說：『如果換衣服的時候覺得害羞，就不要跟其他女生同時間換』、『擔心經血漏出來的話，就使用衛生綿條』。問題不是這些啦，生理期下水讓身體著涼不好啦！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/005325_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F005325_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=eed9afea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 「一位女後輩明明沒有化妝，卻經常被老師責備『妳化妝了吧！！』，還強迫她即場洗臉。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/005433_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F005433_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5c0884a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 「髮圈只能是黑、深藍、啡色。午飯只能帶自家製的便當或麵包，飲品只能夠是日本茶或者牛奶，不能飲紅茶。現在回想起來，能夠遵守這些規矩的自己真厲害呢。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/005537_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F005537_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=0da73c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 「學校禁止穿外套、毛衣，所以天氣寒冷也只能多穿幾件保暖內衣。不過，冬季校服的西裝外套還挺保暖的，但夏季也只能穿這個保暖，整件事超有問題的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/005619_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F005619_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6d0bddc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 「不許談戀愛、不能編麻花辮、假日也不能化妝。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/005717_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F005717_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1a82de37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...etc<br />\n<br />\n借用東京都議員海津敦子的話來作結：校規應該是用作輔助孩子成長，而非作出一些無意義的限制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=6494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6494&d=UEadKhIswHs4snaWK35HW7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8a695f65\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=6494</a>"},{"pid":"7f2d273531ab8c5824742cf002f454bdc0c4f2eb","tid":473961,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"On9五毛又改新聞抹黑"},{"pid":"eff6a8ea8c08c35b0730220c61aafea13c6bdc48","tid":473961,"uid":54876,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"日本人起碼開始反醒，香港人仲以奴性為榮"},{"pid":"258cd3c357485e283bbee7412b73490888f34307","tid":473961,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T23:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本人起碼開始反醒，香港人仲以奴性為榮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de0172967828915bd1d40c2f1d905c59e5b3987","tid":473961,"uid":49392,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:06:06.000Z","msg":"阻止學生妹扮到成隻雞咁，連登仔唔係應該支持咩"},{"pid":"1e68d409dfb00f384bd8a6c9fbba73f9627ab3e1","